    {
        "content": "<p>myunbin opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13205\">PR #13205</a> from <code>myunbin:fix_e-graph_rewrite_depth_limit</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fix an off-by-one in the e-graph rewrite depth limit.</p>\n<p><code>REWRITE_LIMIT</code> is set to 5. Current check uses <code>rewrite_depth &gt; REWRITE_LIMIT</code> before incrementing the depth. Since<br>\n<code>rewrite_depth</code> starts at 0, this allows rewrites to run at effective depth 6.</p>\n<p>If the intended maximum rewrite depth is 5, this changes the check to <code>rewrite_depth &gt;= REWRITE_LIMIT</code>.</p>\n<p>Noticed while investigating #13204.</p>\n</blockquote>",
